Description:    plan - an X/Motif calendar and day planner,
		homepage: http://www.bitrot.de/plan.html
		mailing list: subscribe plan -> majordomo@bitrot.de
Keywords:       plan pland netplan calendar planner appointment network
		alarm reminder scheduler
Author:         thomas@bitrot.de (Thomas Driemeyer)
