Platforms:      SGI IRIX 4,5,6, Linux 2.x, HP/UX 9,10,11, IBM AIX, DEC Unix,
		SunOS 4, Solaris 2, Ultrix, CDC/Mips, RISC/OS, DG/UX, SINIX,
		Interactive Unix, SCO, NCR, USL SVR4, BSDI, NetBSD, FreeBSD,
		Sony NEWS 4,6, Dynix/PTX, Convex BSD, UnixWare 1,2, Apollo/
		DomainOS. Requires Motif or LessTif 0.86.1 libs to compile.
		Static Linux version for Linux without Motif is available.
Copying-policy: freeware, free private and commercial use and copying,
		mandatory credits and change notes
